{"tid":1628943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非踹共] 我支持拆鐵同裝修，但我唔贊成放火","createTime":"2019-10-06T05:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:56:30.000Z","uid":52658,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f93dc6fd1a4cc4064ecd72d68372a17c6fd34616","tid":1628943,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"利申先 我係一個不折不扣既和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就一定係黃 但未到深黃<br />\n您可能覺得我地無吉士 無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但放火始終係國際上面唔係咁好睇<br />\n連一直最撐我地既台灣人都有微言<br />\n燒死人咁點算<br />\n但我就絕對支持餵閘主席食野<br />\n或者拉條黃色水喉入封射壞佢d機件 幫佢自製水舞間<br />\n召喚古希臘神獸都一樣 雖然睇到好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔贊成打撚到佢仆街爆晒江<br />\n但我絕對贊成幫佢剪頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係懲罰您 傷害您 但我無打您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續再放火落去 全世界就會覺得我地係暴徒<br />\n我地都好難做文宣同國際交代<br />\n<br />\n建議黎姐 唔岩聽就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd5e2727b9572c6738a1478abeb23c419062818","tid":1628943,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1d235967c8a88a1df33f4c47364e6aac029b5c","tid":1628943,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1a17cf1140caac6ab48e78ad5f4f3766acacf8","tid":1628943,"uid":327927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"0593e2e9f2d1e61594a784ddb351da5fc73d6423","tid":1628943,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d1a17cf1140caac6ab48e78ad5f4f3766acacf8","tid":1628943,"uid":327927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"係唔會割 唔太贊成姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d978e55dd2d2cc7fcfc54174f16646f4335902b5","tid":1628943,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cfafffc56275c70b32f17134de1f320253587c","tid":1628943,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"c228b5e13ae38715a57d613db59e776441755834","tid":1628943,"uid":128502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"ager"},{"pid":"1c5448cb3c1c9f4b5d2a8a04cda911c5e7bc38ab","tid":1628943,"uid":294343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:50:43.000Z","msg":"一個冇人嘅地鐵站點燒死人"},{"pid":"2f817fb8a59abf4f6869c2af9e3ae833a41b965f","tid":1628943,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"唔係反對。根據當時環境由勇武決定以最低成本裝修方法<br />\n<br />\n等於全世界都反對黑警開鎗一樣。咪又係照開。和理非要負責善後"},{"pid":"1a2071954d16cadd640fdf5385798b8aa17f58fc","tid":1628943,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f817fb8a59abf4f6869c2af9e3ae833a41b965f","tid":1628943,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"唔係反對。根據當時環境由勇武決定以最低成本裝修方法<br />\n<br />\n等於全世界都反對黑警開鎗一樣。咪又係照開。和理非要負責善後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"林奠會唔會同黑警講唔準開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7843a45602258a256482af35c9ea3c6589ac29a","tid":1628943,"uid":28202,"like":1